                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
                    <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <i class="fas fa-quote-left fa-2x text-success opacity-25"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="card-text mb-3">"As a librarian, I love how easy it is to manage the collection and help our community find the perfect book."</p>
